==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Slugging match
<hw>Slug"ging match</hw>. <sd>(a)</sd> <def>A boxing match or prize
fight marked rather by heavy hitting than skill.</def> <mark>[Cant or
Slang]</mark> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>A ball game, esp. a baseball game, in
which there is much hard hitting of the ball.</def> <mark>[Slang, U.
S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Slugging average</ent>⟦br⟧
